      "order": 4,
      "image": "/images/instructions/10-min-halloumi-pittas-with-couscous-salad/step-4.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Slice the <strong>halloumi</strong> into 8 <span class=\"text-danger\">[16]</span> slices</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>halloumi</strong> to the pan and cook for 3-4 min or until golden all over</p>",
