    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once all the water has been absorbed by the couscous and sultanas, add the <strong>juice</strong> of 1/2 <span class=\"text-danger\">[1]</span> <strong>lemon</strong>, 2 tbsp<span class=\"text-danger\"> [4 tbsp]</span><strong> olive oil</strong>, the<strong> flaked almonds</strong> and <strong>chopped parsley</strong> to the <strong>couscous</strong> and give everything a good mix up</p><p>Cut the <strong>remaining lemon</strong> into wedges</p>",
