    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cut the <strong>toasted pitta bread</strong> in half and then stuff them with some <strong>seasonal salad</strong>, <strong>halloumi</strong> and <strong>spicy yoghurt</strong></p><p>Serve the<strong> filled pittas </strong>with the<strong> couscous </strong>and any<strong> remaining salad </strong>to the side</p><p>Drizzle the <strong>salad</strong> with a little <strong>olive oil </strong>and garnish with a wedge of <strong>lemon </strong>and enjoy!</p>",
